wala ka pa bang naiisip na sasalihang org?? here at feucso externals papalawakin natin ang connections mo! kahit ano pang course mo pwede ka dito! if you want to practice your communication skills, we got u here 😍 from reviewing exciting partnership proposals to representing FEU CSO at events, we make sure you’re part of meaningful collaborations within FEU and external partners. 🥰
⭐️ Certificate of Registration (COR, found in student central)
this is your sign, join na! 🫶🏻

message.text:
di ko gagalawin ulo ko, SUMALI NA KAYO FEUCSO EXTERNALS!!
wala ka pa bang naiisip na sasalihang org?? here at feucso externals papalawakin natin ang connections mo! kahit ano pang course mo pwede ka dito! if you want to practice your communication skills, we got u here 😍 from reviewing exciting partnership proposals to representing FEU CSO at events, we make sure you’re part of meaningful collaborations within FEU and external partners. 🥰

GENERAL REQUIREMENTS: 

⭐️ Duly Accomplished Membership Application Form

⭐️ Certificate of Registration (COR, found in student central)

⭐️ Letter of Intent 

⭐️ Curriculum Vitae

JOIN FEUCSO EXTERNALS HERE ⬇️

🔗 https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

this is your sign, join na! 🫶🏻

message.text:
di ko gagalawin ulo ko, SUMALI NA KAYO FEUCSO EXTERNALS!!
wala ka pa bang naiisip na sasalihang org?? here at feucso externals papalawakin natin ang connections mo! kahit ano pang course mo pwede ka dito! if you want to practice your communication skills, we got u here 😍 from reviewing exciting partnership proposals to representing FEU CSO at events, we make sure you’re part of meaningful collaborations within FEU and external partners. 🥰

GENERAL REQUIREMENTS: 

⭐️ Duly Accomplished Membership Application Form

⭐️ Certificate of Registration (COR, found in student central)

⭐️ Letter of Intent 

⭐️ Curriculum Vitae

JOIN FEUCSO EXTERNALS HERE ⬇️

🔗 https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

this is your sign, join na! 🫶🏻
